data.name: label13.ToolTip
data.value: Longer exposure to average noise of over 100db cause serious hearing damge, longer exposure to average noise of over 140db may cause instant serious hearing damage. Examples: - shotgun 170Db, - rocket engine 180Db, - vulcan explosion 200 Db.
